WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-US

00:00:00.470 --> 00:00:03.118
- Things are not impossible,
they're just difficult.

00:00:03.118 --> 00:00:05.701
(upbeat music)

00:00:12.060 --> 00:00:16.190
Hi guys, we're ready to
start our power poses.

00:00:16.190 --> 00:00:18.060
So whenever you're ready, set up your mat.

00:00:18.060 --> 00:00:19.860
You'll start in a child's pose.

00:00:19.860 --> 00:00:21.990
Bring your big toes
together, widen your knees,

00:00:21.990 --> 00:00:24.860
walk the hands forward,
send your hips to your heels

00:00:24.860 --> 00:00:26.260
and rest your forehead down.

00:00:28.440 --> 00:00:30.360
And then inhale, come
forward onto your hands

00:00:30.360 --> 00:00:32.450
and your knees, inhale, arch your spine,

00:00:32.450 --> 00:00:35.200
lift your chest, look up, cow pose.

00:00:35.200 --> 00:00:37.740
And as you exhale, round
and press all the way back

00:00:37.740 --> 00:00:38.883
to your child's pose.

00:00:45.380 --> 00:00:46.790
Find neutral in your spine.

00:00:46.790 --> 00:00:48.720
You're going to activate your palms

00:00:48.720 --> 00:00:50.380
and then pick your knees up a few inches

00:00:50.380 --> 00:00:51.670
off of your mat.

00:00:51.670 --> 00:00:53.200
Look about two feet in front of you.

00:00:53.200 --> 00:00:55.803
Take a full breath in,
draw the low belly in.

00:00:56.730 --> 00:00:59.483
And out, we're here for five, breathe in.

00:01:00.706 --> 00:01:03.623
(optimistic music)

00:01:10.380 --> 00:01:13.040
Tuck your toes and tip
your hips up and back.

00:01:13.040 --> 00:01:15.490
Downward facing dog, good.

00:01:15.490 --> 00:01:18.460
On your next inhale, you'll
come forward to a plank pose.

00:01:18.460 --> 00:01:21.290
Stack your shoulders over your wrists,

00:01:21.290 --> 00:01:24.293
and exhale, make your way
back, downward facing dog.

00:01:25.200 --> 00:01:27.730
And then inhale, come forward to plank.

00:01:27.730 --> 00:01:29.860
Put your left forearm down
so that your elbow goes

00:01:29.860 --> 00:01:32.900
where your palm was,
your right forearm down.

00:01:32.900 --> 00:01:35.070
And then put your left palm down

00:01:35.070 --> 00:01:37.040
and your right palm down.

00:01:37.040 --> 00:01:38.593
Downward facing dog.

00:01:39.590 --> 00:01:41.990
Inhale, come forward to plank.

00:01:41.990 --> 00:01:44.730
Right forearm down, left forearm down.

00:01:44.730 --> 00:01:47.003
This time we're here for five, breathe in.

00:01:48.430 --> 00:01:49.367
And out.

00:01:59.340 --> 00:02:01.310
Exhale, we're coming out of
this the way that we came in.

00:02:01.310 --> 00:02:05.050
So, right palm down and left palm down.

00:02:05.050 --> 00:02:06.573
Downward facing dog.

00:02:07.490 --> 00:02:11.983
Take a full breath in and out.

00:02:13.320 --> 00:02:15.190
Inhale, let's lift your right leg up

00:02:15.190 --> 00:02:17.670
and back behind you, down dog split.

00:02:17.670 --> 00:02:20.830
And as you exhale, bend
your knee and open your hip.

00:02:20.830 --> 00:02:21.930
Inhale, extend your leg

00:02:21.930 --> 00:02:24.070
and turn your toes to face the floor.

00:02:24.070 --> 00:02:26.150
And as you exhale, right
knee to your left tricep.

00:02:26.150 --> 00:02:29.070
So you're crossing your
body, use your obliques.

00:02:29.070 --> 00:02:31.820
Inhale, come all of the way up and back.

00:02:31.820 --> 00:02:34.290
Exhale, bend your knee and open your hip.

00:02:34.290 --> 00:02:37.310
Inhale, extend your legs,
square off your hips,

00:02:37.310 --> 00:02:39.540
and exhale, knee to left tricep

00:02:39.540 --> 00:02:41.500
and then take your right
foot out to the left,

00:02:41.500 --> 00:02:43.860
go along to the inside of the left foot

00:02:43.860 --> 00:02:46.440
and reach your left arm
straight up towards the ceiling.

00:02:46.440 --> 00:02:49.280
Take a full breath in,
in your fallen triangle.

00:02:49.280 --> 00:02:52.070
Exhale, bring your left palm down.

00:02:52.070 --> 00:02:55.110
Bend your right knee, down
dog split as you breathe in.

00:02:55.110 --> 00:02:57.680
Exhale, bend the knee, open the hip.

00:02:57.680 --> 00:03:00.370
Inhale, extend, square off your hips.

00:03:00.370 --> 00:03:02.290
Exhale, coming into your fallen triangle.

00:03:02.290 --> 00:03:04.000
So right knee to your left tricep,

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:05.630
take your foot out to the side,

00:03:05.630 --> 00:03:07.890
reach your left arm straight up

00:03:07.890 --> 00:03:09.890
and now for the challenge you're gonna try

00:03:09.890 --> 00:03:12.220
and pick your foot up off the mat.

00:03:12.220 --> 00:03:13.363
For five.

00:03:15.840 --> 00:03:16.673
Four.

00:03:19.140 --> 00:03:21.253
Three, shaking is a good thing.

00:03:22.930 --> 00:03:23.763
Two.

00:03:25.730 --> 00:03:27.100
And one.

00:03:27.100 --> 00:03:30.653
Left palm down, downward facing dog.

00:03:31.970 --> 00:03:34.853
Good and then don't forget
we have another side.

00:03:37.020 --> 00:03:39.430
You can stay in your downward facing dog,

00:03:39.430 --> 00:03:40.280
we'll meet there.

00:03:41.890 --> 00:03:44.230
On your next inhale, lift your left leg up

00:03:45.240 --> 00:03:48.260
and exhale, bend your
knee and open your hip.

00:03:48.260 --> 00:03:50.450
Inhale back, down dog split.

00:03:50.450 --> 00:03:53.780
And you know the drill, left
knee to your right tricep.

00:03:53.780 --> 00:03:56.280
Inhale, down dog split.

00:03:56.280 --> 00:03:57.863
Bend your knee, open your hip.

00:03:58.840 --> 00:04:01.030
Inhale, down dog split.

00:04:01.030 --> 00:04:03.200
Exhale, left knee to your right tricep.

00:04:03.200 --> 00:04:06.030
Take your foot out to the
side, roll onto the inside

00:04:06.030 --> 00:04:07.460
of your right foot,
reach the right arm up,

00:04:07.460 --> 00:04:11.943
take a full breath in and
exhale, bring that palm down.

00:04:12.900 --> 00:04:15.670
Inhale, down dog split.

00:04:15.670 --> 00:04:18.430
Exhale, bend your knee and open your hip.

00:04:18.430 --> 00:04:20.440
Inhale, down dog split.

00:04:20.440 --> 00:04:22.510
Exhale, left knee to your right tricep.

00:04:22.510 --> 00:04:25.880
Come into your fallen
triangle and then you got it.

00:04:25.880 --> 00:04:27.853
Five breaths, lift the left leg.

00:04:29.241 --> 00:04:32.630
Five.

00:04:32.630 --> 00:04:33.463
Four.

00:04:35.690 --> 00:04:36.523
Three.

00:04:38.760 --> 00:04:39.593
Two.

00:04:41.520 --> 00:04:42.930
And one.

00:04:42.930 --> 00:04:46.323
Right hand down, downward facing dog.

00:04:49.084 --> 00:04:51.103
Knees down and take a seat.

00:04:54.110 --> 00:04:56.680
Thanks for joining us for our power poses.

00:04:56.680 --> 00:04:58.470
You can add these into your flow anytime

00:04:58.470 --> 00:05:00.083
if you wanna add a little fire.

00:05:01.950 --> 00:05:03.301
Namaste.

00:05:03.301 --> 00:05:05.968
(upbeat music)

